<item>
            <title>[SEC-411] SecurityContextHolderAwareRequestWrapper does not define required constructor</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-411</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SecurityContextHolderAwareRequestFilter requires that any request wrapper configured for it must provide a public constructor that accepts two arguments (HttpServletRequest and PortResolver). SecurityContextHolderAwareRequestWrapper does not provide this constructor.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="15681">SEC-411</key>
            <summary>SecurityContextHolderAwareRequestWrapper does not define required constructor</summary>
